The paper discusses the cyber risks associated with IoT and proposes a transformation roadmap for standardization of regulations, risk maturity strategy design, and impact assessment. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of Computer Security (cs.CR) as it deals with cyber risks. Additionally, the paper also discusses the transformation roadmap, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and system integration (cs.SI) aspects. The paper also discusses the impact assessment, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
